Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,yellow,,0,0,0,,http://desuarchive.org/a/thread/155444714/#155446564
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:12.00,yellow,,0,0,0,,12.1話「ばすてき」\NEpisode 12.1 "Bus-ish"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.88,0:00:20.06,yellow,,0,0,0,,ではお前達、これを見つけてくるのです。\NAnd so, you girls are going to look for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.30,0:00:22.75,yellow,,0,0,0,,曲がってない奴を見つけてくるのですよ。\NOne that isn't bent.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.34,0:00:25.80,yellow,,0,0,0,,このまま付けるんじゃダメなのか？\NWhat's wrong with using that one?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.04,0:00:29.36,yellow,,0,0,0,,とりあえず、船にはできる、って聞いたよー。\N｛I heard that it can be made into a boat.｝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.67,0:00:32.36,yellow,,0,0,0,,陸地を走る時に必要なのです。\NIt is necessary when driving on land.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.45,0:00:33.94,yellow,,0,0,0,,頭を使うのです。\NUse your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.17,0:00:35.52,yellow,,0,0,0,,頭を使うのです。\NUse your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.94,0:00:37.48,yellow,,0,0,0,,ちゃんと食べるのですか。\NHave you been eating properly?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.57,0:00:41.08,yellow,,0,0,0,,グヌヌ…！アライさんはその辺ばっちりなのだ！\N｛｝! Arai-san always does!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.54,0:00:44.65,yellow,,0,0,0,,かばんさんの為ならどんとこいだけどさー。\NAlthough you're always ready if it's for Kaban-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.03,0:00:46.96,yellow,,0,0,0,,それって、どこにあるのー？\NWhere do we find those?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.56,0:00:51.49,yellow,,0,0,0,,似たようなバスは、いくつか島で目撃されているのです。\NSimilar buses have been spotted around the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.73,0:00:53.49,yellow,,0,0,0,,まずはそれを探すのです。\NStart by looking for those.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.59,0:00:54.52,yellow,,0,0,0,,探すのです。\NFor those.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.73,0:00:58.28,yellow,,0,0,0,,ちゃんとこれが、真ん丸かどうか、よく見るのですよ。\NLook closely and make sure that this is round.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.62,0:01:02.30,yellow,,0,0,0,,任せるのだ！ピッカピカのを見つけてくるのだ！\NLeave it to Arai-san! I'll find you a really clean one!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.41,0:01:06.47,yellow,,0,0,0,,あー、でもアライさーん、ここんとこ歩きすぎたよー。\NAh, but you've been walking too much lately, Arai-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.66,0:01:08.47,yellow,,0,0,0,,サンドスターがもう…\NYour Sandstar is already…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.61,0:01:12.84,yellow,,0,0,0,,しょうがないですね。遊園地にバス的な物があるのです。\NIt can't be helped. There is a bus-ish thing at the amusement park.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.99,0:01:15.01,yellow,,0,0,0,,バス的な物を貸してやるのです。\NWe'll lend a bus-ish thing to you girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.18,0:01:16.34,yellow,,0,0,0,,とっとと行くのです。\NCome along now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.64,0:01:19.82,yellow,,0,0,0,,何ぃ！？アライさんもバスに乗れるのか！？\NHuh!? You mean, Arai-san gets to ride on a bus too!?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.92,0:01:22.85,yellow,,0,0,0,,おー、よかったねー、アライさーん。\NOh, how nice, Arai-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.45,0:01:25.47,yellow,,0,0,0,,おー！\NOoh!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.47,0:01:27.05,yellow,,0,0,0,,すごーいねー。\NImpressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.63,0:01:31.12,yellow,,0,0,0,,お前らにはそうですね。これぐらいがいいのです。\NThis should be about the right size for you girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.12,0:01:34.92,yellow,,0,0,0,,これくらいなら、足が届くのです。お前らは小さいので。\NYour feet should be able to reach the pedals if it's this big, since you girls are small.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.92,0:01:37.61,yellow,,0,0,0,,ハカセ・ジョシュと似たようなもんだよー。\NJust like you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.61,0:01:39.61,yellow,,0,0,0,,おー！\NOoh!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.53,0:01:46.50,yellow,,0,0,0,,わっせ、わっせ、わっせ…\NHeave-ho, heave-ho, heave-ho…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.09,0:01:49.54,yellow,,0,0,0,,出発！…なのだ！\NLet's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.54,0:01:51.14,yellow,,0,0,0,,はーいよ、っと。\NMm.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.62,0:01:54.40,yellow,,0,0,0,,わっせ、わっせ、わっせ…\NHeave-ho, heave-ho, heave-ho…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.40,0:01:56.83,yellow,,0,0,0,,歩くのとそんなに変わらないのです。\NIt's really not that different from walking.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.83,0:01:59.87,yellow,,0,0,0,,あれは船出に間に合いますか、ハカセ。\NDo you think they'll make it before they set sail?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.87,0:02:03.82,yellow,,0,0,0,,まあ、なんだかんだ。あの根性を信用してるのです。\NI think they'll get it done. I trust in their spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.82,0:02:05.95,yellow,,0,0,0,,大丈夫ですよ、ジョシュ。\NIt'll be alright, Assistant.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.60,0:02:08.61,yellow,,0,0,0,,これで概ね片付きましたね。\NThis should be the last of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.61,0:02:11.33,yellow,,0,0,0,,まったく。長も楽じゃないのです。\NGoodness. It's not easy being a chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.33,0:02:16.11,yellow,,0,0,0,,これで長らしく果報を食べて待てるのです。まったく。\NI suppose all we can do now is ｛｝. Goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.11,0:02:19.11,yellow,,0,0,0,,今日もかばんにご馳走になりますか。ハカセ。\NWill we be partaking of Kaban's cooking again? Professor.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.11,0:02:23.75,yellow,,0,0,0,,そうですね。ちょっと料理を引っ掛けて帰りますか、ジョシュ。\NIndeed. Shall we go to oversee it?
